00:55:41.250 --> 00:55:47.650
famous for its tower-like hills called Mugoltes. Caves and rivers run through many of them.

00:55:48.690 --> 00:55:56.050
The Estade Minyales congregation is located in this part of Cuba. Here 128 publishers

00:55:56.130 --> 00:56:03.329
conduct 275 Bible studies. Because of its vast territory, the congregation has three groups.

00:56:04.289 --> 00:56:10.690
One group that has only seven publishers had 75 people attend last year's memorial.

00:56:11.570 --> 00:56:18.530
To cover their territory, the brothers travel long distances, sometimes by bicycle or motorcycle.

00:56:19.650 --> 00:56:24.690
They witness to people wherever they are on farms and in their homes.

00:56:26.210 --> 00:56:32.449
The brothers enjoy Christian fellowship, good coffee, and singing songs of praise to Jehovah.

00:56:33.250 --> 00:56:38.769
Our brothers and sisters in the Estade Minyales congregation send their love to the

00:56:38.769 --> 00:56:45.889
worldwide Brotherhood. From the World Headquarters of Jehovah's Witnesses, this is J.W. Broadcasting.
